      <p id="JqpdVe" outputclass="Normal">B. Enter Name of Assessing Official:</p>
      <p id="ebooEs" outputclass="Normal">The Assessing Official may input ratings and narrative, sign the assessment report, and release it to the contractor, and modify the report following contractor comments or close the report if it is not contentious. The Assessing Official is the person with overall responsibility for the program/project or job/task/delivery order. The Assessing Official must be a U.S. Army employee.</p>
